  m_Name: Boxer
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Character
  characterName: Dude
  health: 150
  attack: 3
  defence: 2
  ultimate: 25
  attackDescription: Powerful close-range punches with solid burst damage.
  defenseDescription: Can withstand more hits than a regular character thanks to
    a tight boxing guard.
  speedDescription: not the fastest, but far from slow.
  ultimateDescription: "a rapid flurry of punches delivered like he\u2019s dropping
    off packages straight to the opponent\u2019s face."
  story: "Boxer is an ordinary guy from the neighborhood who trained in an old gym.
    He\u2019s not a superhero or a mutant \u2014 just a tough man who knows how to
    take a hit and return it twice as hard. His ultimate, Postman, is a legendary
    combo he invented back when he worked as a courier."
  shortDescription: "A tough close\u2011range fighter with solid durability and a
    signature flurry attack called Postman."
